      "name": "VAD hemolysis adequacy claim",
      "description": "The CFD model adequately predicts absolute hemolysis index values for the Class III VAD device across all five evaluated flow-speed operating points, supporting the conclusion that predicted hemolysis remains below the established clinical threshold.",
      "purpose": "Establish that the simulation-based hemolysis predictions are sufficiently credible to inform regulatory acceptance for the VAD device.",
      "scope": "Absolute hemolysis index predictions at MRL 5 for a centrifugal blood pump under VAD operating conditions."
    }
  ],
